{
  "texts": [
    "To ensure that the dataset also represented those flows in a meaningful enough manner that allows models to learn to address those requests, we increased the likelihood of any non-navigational intent occurring.",
    "In particular, we increased the probability of Questions, Fun Facts, Definition Questions, Replacements, Fallbacks, and Chit Chats.",
    "As described in Section 4, for most intents, the user utterances are extracted from the interactions considered to create this dataset.",
    "The considered interactions were any interaction where the user had started a recipe and spent at least 2 turns doing it.",
    "For each intent, we collected all utterances identified by our intent classifier, the most common 100 are then manually annotated to clean up any classification errors, personally identifiable information, and offensive language."
  ]
}